<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      body {
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f7fa;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 30px 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header h1 {
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
      }
      .greeting {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .otp-section {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        border-left: 4px solid #f5576c;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 25px 0;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
      .otp-label {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #666;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        display: block;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      .otp-code {
        font-size: 36px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #f5576c;
        letter-spacing: 3px;
        text-align: center;
        font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
      }
      .expiry-info {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #e74c3c;
        margin-top: 15px;
        text-align: center;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      .instructions {
        background-color: #e8f4f8;
        border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #2c3e50;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .instructions ol {
        margin-left: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }
      .instructions li {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 20px 30px;
        border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #999;
        text-align: center;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .warning {
        background-color: #f8d7da;
        border-left: 4px solid #f5576c;
        padding: 15px;
        margin-top: 20px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        color: #721c24;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      .warning strong {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>üîê Password Reset</h1>
        <p>Reset your account password</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <div class="greeting">
          <strong>Hello <%= name %>,</strong><br /><br />
          We received a request to reset your password. To proceed with
          resetting your password, please use the OTP code below.
        </div>

        <div class="otp-section">
          <span class="otp-label">Your Reset Code</span>
          <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
          <div class="expiry-info">‚è∞ This code expires in 10 minutes</div>
        </div>

        <div class="instructions">
          <strong>How to reset your password:</strong>
          <ol>
            <li>Copy the reset code above</li>
            <li>
              Return to our platform and navigate to the password reset page
            </li>
            <li>Enter the code along with your new password</li>
            <li>Click "Reset Password" to confirm</li>
          </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="warning">
          <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important Security Notice:</strong>
          <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 8px">
            <li>
              If you didn't request this, ignore this email and your account
              remains secure
            </li>
            <li>Never share your reset code with anyone</li>
            <li>We will never ask for your password via email</li>
            <li>Make sure to create a strong, unique password</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p style="color: #555; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 20px">
          If you need any assistance or have questions, please contact our
          support team.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.<br />
          If you did not request a password reset, please secure your account
          immediately.<br /><br />
          ¬© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Tech Jaunt. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
